-Teltoli-

She stands still in almost shock. First Carnage had come out and stood in front of her, then Tritan came out and nearly died for her, and handed her a disk which she still had in her hand. Then Shocker insulted her. Ooohh that last one really blew her nerves, she thought angrily. As he walked away she pulled out her gun and aim at his back, and fired, not really caring if she hit or not.

"Oh" She says finally, optics still slightly rounded from surprise. Then she berates herself irratably. She only noticed the burn mark on her shoulder a few seconds later.

Teltoli shakes her head. "OK what happened? They're coming, they're going, one gets nearly slagged for me.. Carnage?"

She turned to her friend for answers, still looking surprised and dazed..
